      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nBuild Successful \n\nhttps://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/78801/ : SUCCESS\n\nhttps://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews-patchless/18769/ : SUCCESS",
